description: Enferno Storm Commerce API Client library.
releaseNotes:
## What's new?

### OrderService:
- #2657: New, or modified, entities and methods now exist for Invoices. New methods are GetInvoice and ListInvoices. New entities are InvoicePagedList and InvoiceListItem. Invoice and InvoiceItem have been modified slightly.  
https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Invoices/ListInvoices  
https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Invoices/GetInvoice   
https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Invoices/InvoicePagedList  
https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Invoices/InvoiceListItem  
https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Invoices/Invoice  
https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Invoices/InvoiceItem  

## What's fixed?

### OrderService:
- #2212: Due to performance problems with OrderList and ListOrders, ListOrder2 they have now been deprecated. There is now a new ListOrders3 with a more light weight resultset, OrderPagedList2 with items as OrderListItem. Basically all references to DeliveryNotes have been removed from list results. The Order entity should be unchanged.  
https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Orders/ListOrders3  
https://servicesstage.enferno.se/api/1.1/docs/index2.html#/Orders/Orders/OrderListItem  

## Miscellaneous changes?

- #2664: We now have an API client for PHP which is located at  
https://github.com/StormCommerce/Storm.API-client-php  
It can be used by those building solutions using PHP.

Regards,  
The Storm API Team
